name: 阿布舍克·德斯瓦尔
name_full: 阿布舍克·德斯瓦尔 Abhishek Deswal
introduction: Abhishek Deswal is an Indian actor who primarily works in the Indian Film Industry. He works across mediums and has acted in several notable theatrical productions-A Farming Story, Bone of Contention in Cosmopolitan Cooperative Housing Society, and The Tales of the Widowmaker. A movement enthusiast, he believes in equal rights & humor.
